# [AVTCORE](../wg/avtcore.html)

## Summary

The AVTCORE working group met at IETF 126. The session covered status updates on working group drafts, followed by presentations and technical discussions on frame acknowledgement, RTP payload formats for V-DMC, RTP/SDP signaling for multichannel Opus, and a new SRTP cipher suite utilizing GCM-SST.

